message: Absolutely delicious! The jalebis came out perfectly crispy and soaked the syrup beautifully. The fafda was light and crunchy—just like the traditional street-side taste. Loved it!
The jalebi and fafda tasted good, but the jalebi could have been a bit more crisp. Overall it was enjoyable and worth trying.
The dish turned out really good! Jalebi had the perfect texture and the fafda had that classic flavor. My family enjoyed it a lot. Will definitely make this again!
Great recipe! The steps were easy to follow, and the results were amazing. Jalebi sweetness and fafda crispiness were well balanced. A must-try for festive mornings!
The taste was okay but not great. The fafda felt a little too hard, and the jalebi wasn’t as crispy as expected. Overall, it could be improved
Jalebi was sweet but lacked freshness, and the fafda was slightly oily. Not bad, but definitely not what I was hoping for
